        </div>
     </div>
     <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="picturing">
          <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/ccmcoversbsc/On-site+classes.png" alt="Class Scene" align="middle">
          <div class="col-md-13 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-offset-2 col-sm-10 icon-text-box">
            <h4>Step 3: Invite other potential volunteers!</h4>
            <p>With the huge demand for English by Thai students, we are always looking for new volunteers to join us!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
     </div>
  </div>
